1
00:00:00,020 --> 00:00:05,080
♪ Inside the state a city is built ♪

2
00:00:05,080 --> 00:00:10,190
♪ Where a benevolent emperor resides ♪

3
00:00:10,190 --> 00:00:15,330
♪ Court officials are brave and able ♪

4
00:00:15,330 --> 00:00:22,750
♪ The empress is fair ♪

5
00:00:25,580 --> 00:00:30,710
♪ Princes died too young to ascend the throne ♪

6
00:00:30,710 --> 00:00:35,570
♪ Princesses are spoiled and fragile ♪

7
00:00:35,840 --> 00:00:40,270
♪ Commoners are also the emperor’s children ♪

8
00:00:40,830 --> 00:00:49,630
♪ All are living peacefully ♪

9
00:00:49,930 --> 00:00:54,280
♪ Wish I could live a day for myself ♪

10
00:00:55,000 --> 00:00:59,380
♪ Follow my heart and ethics without distractions ♪

11
00:01:00,710 --> 00:01:03,400
♪ To be a good husband ♪

12
00:01:03,400 --> 00:01:05,970
♪ To be a caring father ♪

13
00:01:06,460 --> 00:01:10,110
♪ We were close when we first met ♪

14
00:01:10,460 --> 00:01:14,710
♪ I hope I can control my desires ♪

15
00:01:15,540 --> 00:01:20,060
♪ To be a worriless emperor and father ♪

16
00:01:21,120 --> 00:01:23,860
♪ Prudence tops all virtues ♪

17
00:01:23,860 --> 00:01:26,480
♪ People build the state ♪

18
00:01:26,750 --> 00:01:30,020
= Held in the Lonely Castle =
♪ May the world be peaceful ♪

19
00:01:30,020 --> 00:01:33,020
= Episode 45 =

20
00:01:43,340 --> 00:01:44,740
How’s mother been lately?

21
00:01:45,540 --> 00:01:46,780
Dose her back still hurt?

22
00:01:47,420 --> 00:01:49,300
Thanks to Your Highness’s medicine,

23
00:01:49,300 --> 00:01:50,260
she’s feeling much better.

24
00:01:51,420 --> 00:01:53,380
You got a fine zither last month, didn’t you?

25
00:01:53,900 --> 00:01:55,060
Is it well-tuned?

26
00:01:55,900 --> 00:01:56,700
Lately, I’ve been too busy

27
00:01:56,900 --> 00:01:58,180
to play the instrument.

28
00:01:58,500 --> 00:02:00,700
Ping’s is more skilled than before.

29
00:02:01,020 --> 00:02:01,980
After some time,

30
00:02:01,980 --> 00:02:03,420
= Cao Yi =
he’ll be even better than me.

31
00:02:05,940 --> 00:02:08,300
You’re spoiling Ping too much.

32
00:02:09,140 --> 00:02:10,100
He’s smart,

33
00:02:10,660 --> 00:02:12,700
but impatient and pleasure-seeking.

34
00:02:15,140 --> 00:02:17,180
I’ll discipline him.

35
00:02:21,460 --> 00:02:22,820
Thank you for your instruction, aunt.

36
00:02:24,260 --> 00:02:24,980
Rise.

37
00:02:27,220 --> 00:02:28,020
Ping, You,

38
00:02:28,540 --> 00:02:29,460
come closer.

39
00:02:38,260 --> 00:02:41,100
= Cao Yi’s Son Cao Ping =
= Cao Ping’s Younger Brother Cao You =

40
00:02:42,940 --> 00:02:43,780
Hou Yi!

41
00:02:59,740 --> 00:03:02,100
Comb my hair to freshen me up.

42
00:03:02,540 --> 00:03:03,660
Sima Guang nagged me

43
00:03:03,660 --> 00:03:04,620
for almost four hours.

44
00:03:04,860 --> 00:03:06,940
My head is stuffed.

45
00:03:08,540 --> 00:03:09,380
No wonder Mr. Sima

46
00:03:10,100 --> 00:03:11,740
can teach at the Directorate of Education.

47
00:03:13,380 --> 00:03:14,980
Other than the same old platitudes,

48
00:03:15,460 --> 00:03:17,460
he said something new.

49
00:03:18,313 --> 00:03:19,700
Over the past decade,

50
00:03:20,620 --> 00:03:23,060
he’s been the first court official

51
00:03:23,100 --> 00:03:24,260
to impeach the Empress.

52
00:03:26,020 --> 00:03:27,460
- Impeach the Empress? - Impeach the Empress?

53
00:03:27,860 --> 00:03:28,860
- Why? - Why?

54
00:03:34,580 --> 00:03:35,860
He listed 15 statements.

55
00:03:36,340 --> 00:03:38,140
14 of them

56
00:03:38,140 --> 00:03:39,220
were criticisms of my mistakes,

57
00:03:39,220 --> 00:03:40,260
which didn’t surprise you at all.

58
00:03:40,740 --> 00:03:42,060
But the one about the Empress

59
00:03:42,300 --> 00:03:43,660
almost made you jump.

60
00:03:46,140 --> 00:03:47,300
Clearly,

61
00:03:48,140 --> 00:03:49,660
the Empress is much better than me.

62
00:03:52,580 --> 00:03:53,500
I’m so sorry, Your Majesty.

63
00:03:58,940 --> 00:03:59,700
Rise.

64
00:04:06,340 --> 00:04:07,700
Sima Guang accused the Empress

65
00:04:08,700 --> 00:04:10,460
of being unable to discipline her relatives.

66
00:04:11,940 --> 00:04:14,500
She indulged her nephew Cao Ping’s wild behavior.

67
00:04:15,380 --> 00:04:16,940
He’s fond of riding and music,

68
00:04:17,060 --> 00:04:18,220
and also a patron at music houses.

69
00:04:19,060 --> 00:04:22,500
He’s extremely popular among girls there

70
00:04:23,020 --> 00:04:24,980
who are eager to serve him.

71
00:04:25,820 --> 00:04:26,540
Also, he’s well-known

72
00:04:26,540 --> 00:04:28,380
among girls of noble birth.

73
00:04:29,300 --> 00:04:31,380
They’re all painting him.

74
00:04:35,740 --> 00:04:37,020
Funniest of all,

75
00:04:37,820 --> 00:04:39,500
rich merchants from Hangzhou

76
00:04:39,540 --> 00:04:41,940
mistook him as a male escort

77
00:04:42,300 --> 00:04:43,660
and insisted on bringing him back home.

78
00:04:44,380 --> 00:04:45,860
It’s a huge mess

79
00:04:46,140 --> 00:04:49,100
which disgraces the Empress’s family

80
00:04:50,060 --> 00:04:51,220
and induces more criticisms.

81
00:04:53,660 --> 00:04:55,140
Mr. Cao must be

82
00:04:55,380 --> 00:04:56,740
extremely handsome.

83
00:04:58,140 --> 00:04:59,660
Cao Ping is good-looking,

84
00:04:59,900 --> 00:05:01,660
and smart, an all-round talent.

85
00:05:02,380 --> 00:05:03,700
His grandmother dotes on him

86
00:05:04,660 --> 00:05:07,500
and doesn’t want to restrict him too much.

87
00:05:09,140 --> 00:05:09,860
But

88
00:05:10,420 --> 00:05:12,140
he’s still a teenager.

89
00:05:12,660 --> 00:05:14,980
Those rumors are too much,

90
00:05:16,060 --> 00:05:17,020
which even drew Sima Guang’s attention

91
00:05:17,020 --> 00:05:18,540
who specially wrote a proposal

92
00:05:19,020 --> 00:05:20,140
to exaggerate it even further.

93
00:05:23,380 --> 00:05:24,700
His articles

94
00:05:25,540 --> 00:05:26,540
often surprise me.

95
00:05:27,420 --> 00:05:28,460
He’s insightful

96
00:05:28,740 --> 00:05:30,340
and indeed wise.

97
00:05:31,420 --> 00:05:33,420
But what he said in front of me...

98
00:05:39,340 --> 00:05:40,620
No other young masters

99
00:05:41,020 --> 00:05:42,060
would go up there and play god

100
00:05:42,420 --> 00:05:44,100
at the Gods Receiving Festival.

101
00:05:45,020 --> 00:05:46,340
Even princess remembers that.

102
00:05:47,140 --> 00:05:48,700
Clearly, you were way out of the line

103
00:05:48,940 --> 00:05:49,980
in front of others.

104
00:05:54,740 --> 00:05:57,060
Back then, he was just around 14 years old

105
00:05:57,540 --> 00:05:58,780
and only did that for fun.

106
00:05:59,260 --> 00:06:00,460
Huirou shouldn’t have brought it up.

107
00:06:00,660 --> 00:06:01,660
Otherwise, you wouldn’t

108
00:06:01,900 --> 00:06:03,540
have been angered by the past.

109
00:06:05,700 --> 00:06:06,580
Huirou, come here.

110
00:06:06,860 --> 00:06:07,780
Meet your cousin.

111
00:06:12,740 --> 00:06:13,780
This is Cousin Ping.

112
00:06:16,460 --> 00:06:17,420
Cousin Ping.

113
00:06:18,220 --> 00:06:19,220
This is Cousin You.

114
00:06:20,700 --> 00:06:21,660
Cousin You.

115
00:06:24,460 --> 00:06:25,300
Princess.

116
00:06:26,300 --> 00:06:27,140
Princess.

117
00:06:29,900 --> 00:06:30,540
Your Highness,

118
00:06:30,620 --> 00:06:32,340
may I go play with Cousin You at the backyard?

119
00:06:33,540 --> 00:06:34,460
Go ahead.

120
00:06:37,740 --> 00:06:38,340
Let’s go.

121
00:06:43,420 --> 00:06:44,420
Go with them, Ping.

122
00:06:45,300 --> 00:06:46,060
Yes.

123
00:06:50,380 --> 00:06:52,460
Huaiji, follow them

124
00:06:52,820 --> 00:06:53,860
and take care of princess.

125
00:07:23,460 --> 00:07:24,460
Princess, do you want to try it?

126
00:07:27,420 --> 00:07:28,420
I don’t know how.

127
00:07:29,180 --> 00:07:29,900
I know.

128
00:07:36,660 --> 00:07:37,980
Do you also excel at this ball game?

129
00:07:38,620 --> 00:07:39,740
See it yourself.

130
00:08:03,580 --> 00:08:04,476
Well done!

131
00:08:04,497 --> 00:08:05,780
Impressive!

132
00:08:07,380 --> 00:08:09,102
He’s really good!

133
00:08:10,587 --> 00:08:12,013
One more. Do it again.

134
00:08:18,180 --> 00:08:19,500
You’re good, Cao.

135
00:08:24,726 --> 00:08:26,260
You’re excellent!

136
00:08:27,580 --> 00:08:28,780
Can you teach me, Cao?

137
00:08:28,806 --> 00:08:29,356
Come here.

138
00:08:34,260 --> 00:08:35,380
Hold it like this.

139
00:08:40,295 --> 00:08:42,240
- Amazing! - You’re so good, Cao!

140
00:08:42,260 --> 00:08:43,391
Great!

141
00:09:02,260 --> 00:09:04,380
How did I do, princess?

142
00:09:07,380 --> 00:09:08,500
Would you like to have a try?

143
00:09:10,500 --> 00:09:11,540
I don’t think I can.

144
00:09:12,380 --> 00:09:13,140
I can help you.

145
00:09:13,820 --> 00:09:15,700
Please teach me.

146
00:09:22,500 --> 00:09:23,140
Aunt.

147
00:09:24,220 --> 00:09:26,340
= The Elder Princess of Wei =

148
00:09:26,340 --> 00:09:27,100
I heard

149
00:09:27,260 --> 00:09:28,900
from the Head of Imperial Hospital, Mr. Wang,

150
00:09:29,420 --> 00:09:30,220
that your eyes

151
00:09:30,220 --> 00:09:31,580
hurt again earlier.

152
00:09:33,500 --> 00:09:34,540
Please have a seat, aunt.

153
00:09:34,540 --> 00:09:35,180
Thank you.

154
00:09:37,660 --> 00:09:39,060
Your stomach is weak, too.

155
00:09:39,580 --> 00:09:41,420
Is it because

156
00:09:41,420 --> 00:09:42,460
you can’t eat properly?

157
00:09:42,900 --> 00:09:45,460
I can send two eunuchs who have medical knowledge

158
00:09:45,620 --> 00:09:47,020
and can cook herbal cuisine

159
00:09:47,020 --> 00:09:48,140
to look after you.

160
00:09:49,300 --> 00:09:50,580
When people get old,

161
00:09:50,620 --> 00:09:52,300
diseases will catch up.

162
00:09:52,580 --> 00:09:54,180
Don’t worry about me.

163
00:09:55,340 --> 00:09:56,340
Please stop

164
00:09:56,420 --> 00:09:58,660
rewarding me with expensive gifts

165
00:09:58,660 --> 00:09:59,940
or ingredients.

166
00:10:00,340 --> 00:10:02,740
They are too much for me.

167
00:10:03,740 --> 00:10:05,060
Since my husband passed away,

168
00:10:05,340 --> 00:10:07,660
I’ve stopped using

169
00:10:07,820 --> 00:10:09,140
pearls or jade.

170
00:10:11,740 --> 00:10:14,780
I do have one request, though.

171
00:10:16,820 --> 00:10:17,740
What is it?

172
00:10:19,940 --> 00:10:21,860
My husband’s youngest daughter

173
00:10:22,060 --> 00:10:23,380
is 16 years old.

174
00:10:23,940 --> 00:10:26,220
She lost her mother not long ago

175
00:10:26,620 --> 00:10:28,300
and was all alone,

176
00:10:29,020 --> 00:10:30,540
so I took the liberty

177
00:10:30,820 --> 00:10:32,340
to bring her back.

178
00:10:33,220 --> 00:10:36,700
She’s old enough to marry.

179
00:10:37,260 --> 00:10:40,100
Please allow me

180
00:10:40,220 --> 00:10:41,660
to adopt her

181
00:10:42,300 --> 00:10:43,380
to be a member of our family,

182
00:10:43,500 --> 00:10:45,340
so that she can marry a decent husband.

183
00:10:52,100 --> 00:10:53,220
That’s too kind of you, aunt.

184
00:10:54,620 --> 00:10:57,180
I have no reason to stop you,

185
00:10:58,660 --> 00:10:59,420
but

186
00:11:00,860 --> 00:11:02,140
back then, when your husband

187
00:11:02,340 --> 00:11:04,180
already had wife and concubines,

188
00:11:04,900 --> 00:11:06,740
he fathered a daughter with a babysitter.

189
00:11:07,300 --> 00:11:08,700
You interceded with me for him.

190
00:11:09,620 --> 00:11:11,660
But he continued

191
00:11:11,700 --> 00:11:13,260
to fool around with dancers and singers.

192
00:11:14,300 --> 00:11:17,620
I was mad that he mistreated you like this,

193
00:11:17,700 --> 00:11:18,820
so I forbade him

194
00:11:18,820 --> 00:11:20,060
from taking that woman in.

195
00:11:20,340 --> 00:11:21,060
Her children...

196
00:11:21,060 --> 00:11:22,100
He already died,

197
00:11:22,660 --> 00:11:25,740
so his sins have been buried with him.

198
00:11:26,900 --> 00:11:28,500
He was my husband after all.

199
00:11:28,660 --> 00:11:29,820
Taking care of his children

200
00:11:30,340 --> 00:11:32,380
is also my responsibility.

201
00:11:46,540 --> 00:11:49,180
Madam, let me help you tidy up.

202
00:11:52,100 --> 00:11:54,300
I won’t attend the dinner banquet.

203
00:11:56,100 --> 00:11:57,700
Why?

204
00:11:58,500 --> 00:12:00,500
Relatives and noble ladies will all be there.

205
00:12:00,740 --> 00:12:02,100
A grand celebration like this is rare.

206
00:12:03,620 --> 00:12:05,500
Who are you to lecture me?

207
00:12:06,740 --> 00:12:07,940
His Majesty already said

208
00:12:08,580 --> 00:12:09,460
I don’t have to

209
00:12:10,620 --> 00:12:13,500
attend such events.

210
00:12:15,500 --> 00:12:18,540
His Majesty’s adopted son
is marrying the Empress’s adopted daughter.

211
00:12:19,500 --> 00:12:21,220
They’re all celebrating it.

212
00:12:22,300 --> 00:12:25,580
Those guests are all flattering them

213
00:12:25,740 --> 00:12:27,380
and showering them with compliments.

214
00:12:28,220 --> 00:12:29,860
They make me sick.

215
00:12:30,460 --> 00:12:31,660
That marriage alliance

216
00:12:32,460 --> 00:12:33,580
is a joke.

217
00:12:35,700 --> 00:12:37,220
His Majesty and the Empress
have been married for years.

218
00:12:38,820 --> 00:12:39,780
How come they don’t have

219
00:12:39,780 --> 00:12:41,460
even one child together?

220
00:12:42,660 --> 00:12:44,740
I can’t agree more with you, madam!

221
00:12:45,500 --> 00:12:46,780
I bet

222
00:12:46,900 --> 00:12:47,940
others think so.

223
00:12:49,340 --> 00:12:50,020
By the way,

224
00:12:50,340 --> 00:12:51,500
let me share something funny

225
00:12:51,580 --> 00:12:52,780
with you.

226
00:12:53,740 --> 00:12:54,500
What is it?

227
00:12:55,420 --> 00:12:56,300
It’s said

228
00:12:56,380 --> 00:12:58,260
earlier today, a knowledgeable

229
00:12:59,100 --> 00:13:01,220
and honest official, who’s adored by His Majesty,

230
00:13:02,340 --> 00:13:03,700
impeached the Empress.

231
00:13:05,700 --> 00:13:06,700
He impeached the Empress?

232
00:13:10,380 --> 00:13:12,380
Finally, there’s an official who isn’t blind.

233
00:13:13,100 --> 00:13:15,580
What did he accuse her? Hypocrisy and deception?

234
00:13:54,060 --> 00:13:55,260
Your Majesty seems a bit upset.

235
00:13:57,420 --> 00:13:58,900
When you were greeting Elder Princess

236
00:13:58,900 --> 00:14:00,060
and other seniors,

237
00:14:01,300 --> 00:14:04,140
was any of them feeling unwell?

238
00:14:06,940 --> 00:14:08,180
I’m just thinking

239
00:14:09,900 --> 00:14:11,380
my aunt is a princess

240
00:14:11,620 --> 00:14:12,940
who’s elegant and tender,

241
00:14:14,140 --> 00:14:15,540
but the man she married

242
00:14:15,540 --> 00:14:17,140
was a disgrace.

243
00:14:19,460 --> 00:14:21,260
Life is too hard on her.

244
00:14:24,380 --> 00:14:25,620
Aunt is virtuous and kindhearted,

245
00:14:26,620 --> 00:14:28,340
a role model for all women.

246
00:14:29,700 --> 00:14:31,060
Deep down inside, Elder Princess

247
00:14:32,220 --> 00:14:33,340
is in pain.

248
00:14:33,940 --> 00:14:35,780
= Gao Taotao =
What kind of person was her husband?

249
00:14:36,420 --> 00:14:39,060
Grandaunt must love him dearly.

250
00:15:00,380 --> 00:15:02,220
Lady Zhang, you look radiant today.

251
00:15:03,500 --> 00:15:04,660
Have you recovered?

252
00:15:05,780 --> 00:15:06,580
I’m fine.

253
00:15:07,620 --> 00:15:09,420
I had a headache

254
00:15:09,900 --> 00:15:11,500
and a stomachache in the morning,

255
00:15:11,660 --> 00:15:12,740
and didn’t want to move.

256
00:15:13,940 --> 00:15:17,100
Then I heard about the banquet at the backyard

257
00:15:18,340 --> 00:15:20,340
for The Thirteenth Prince and Miss Gao’s wedding.

258
00:15:21,340 --> 00:15:24,620
Your Majesty and Your Highness are in-laws now.

259
00:15:25,580 --> 00:15:27,500
This can’t be missed.

260
00:15:29,540 --> 00:15:30,780
I also heard

261
00:15:32,860 --> 00:15:34,380
there’s someone even better.

262
00:15:37,980 --> 00:15:39,100
I was told

263
00:15:39,500 --> 00:15:41,060
that Your Highness’s nephew also came.

264
00:15:42,620 --> 00:15:43,900
It’s said

265
00:15:45,020 --> 00:15:46,140
Mr. Cao’s reputation

266
00:15:46,740 --> 00:15:48,420
is widely recognized.

267
00:15:50,460 --> 00:15:52,140
Every time he rides in the street,

268
00:15:52,900 --> 00:15:55,020
girls will throw handkerchiefs, sachets

269
00:15:55,700 --> 00:15:57,260
and even underwear at him.

270
00:15:59,580 --> 00:16:00,940
I was intrigued

271
00:16:01,820 --> 00:16:02,900
and eager

272
00:16:03,820 --> 00:16:05,540
to find out how excellent he is,

273
00:16:07,460 --> 00:16:08,460
so I managed

274
00:16:09,140 --> 00:16:10,540
to get out of bed

275
00:16:11,220 --> 00:16:13,860
and came here.

276
00:16:14,700 --> 00:16:15,500
Enough.

277
00:16:17,180 --> 00:16:18,340
Since you don’t feel well,

278
00:16:19,060 --> 00:16:20,260
just sit and rest.

279
00:16:21,340 --> 00:16:23,140
I can’t believe you were misled by rumors

280
00:16:23,300 --> 00:16:24,860
and only came to see if they were true.

281
00:16:27,540 --> 00:16:28,700
Rules of the harem

282
00:16:29,140 --> 00:16:30,100
seem to be loose.

283
00:16:36,060 --> 00:16:37,220
It’s my fault.

284
00:16:37,820 --> 00:16:39,780
I’ll tighten the grip.

285
00:16:40,540 --> 00:16:41,900
They aren’t rumors.

286
00:16:42,820 --> 00:16:44,460
He is as good as they say.

287
00:16:46,220 --> 00:16:47,260
Others aside,

288
00:16:48,060 --> 00:16:49,740
look at Princess Fukang.

289
00:16:50,780 --> 00:16:52,780
She usually stays with her father

290
00:16:54,020 --> 00:16:55,980
all the time at banquets

291
00:16:56,700 --> 00:16:58,540
and never goes out

292
00:16:58,540 --> 00:16:59,340
to play with boys.

293
00:17:01,780 --> 00:17:02,820
But now,

294
00:17:05,740 --> 00:17:09,980
where is she?

295
00:18:01,420 --> 00:18:02,380
As a beginner,

296
00:18:02,380 --> 00:18:03,140
you’ve done

297
00:18:03,140 --> 00:18:04,340
good enough, princess.

298
00:18:06,700 --> 00:18:07,500
I’ll go get it.

299
00:18:30,780 --> 00:18:31,420
You,

300
00:18:31,740 --> 00:18:33,300
pass me the ball, please.

301
00:18:33,300 --> 00:18:34,060
Sure.

302
00:18:36,700 --> 00:18:37,620
Place your hands like this.

303
00:18:44,620 --> 00:18:45,300
Like this?

304
00:19:07,780 --> 00:19:09,580
Kids love playing games.

305
00:19:34,420 --> 00:19:35,260
Sir,

306
00:19:35,820 --> 00:19:37,180
were you hit badly?

307
00:19:38,260 --> 00:19:39,220
I’m fine.

308
00:19:40,460 --> 00:19:41,260
I’m alright.

309
00:19:42,580 --> 00:19:44,940
Put down your hand. Let me see.

310
00:19:49,740 --> 00:19:51,860
Relax. It just looks a bit red.

311
00:19:52,860 --> 00:19:53,940
Princess!

312
00:19:54,460 --> 00:19:55,340
Coming.

313
00:19:58,620 --> 00:19:59,540
= Li Wei, courtesy name Gongzhao =
Let’s continue.

314
00:19:59,900 --> 00:20:00,660
Sure.

315
00:20:00,660 --> 00:20:01,380
Sir,

316
00:20:02,460 --> 00:20:03,500
I’m really sorry.

317
00:20:03,620 --> 00:20:04,780
If it hurts,

318
00:20:04,820 --> 00:20:06,740
I can call an Imperial Physician for you.

319
00:20:06,980 --> 00:20:07,860
Thank you.

320
00:20:14,780 --> 00:20:17,900
Is...is she Huirou?

321
00:20:17,900 --> 00:20:18,700
Go get the ball.

322
00:20:21,900 --> 00:20:23,060
That’s Princess Fukang.

323
00:20:26,500 --> 00:20:27,220
Mr. Li,

324
00:20:27,660 --> 00:20:28,820
Lord Li is looking for you.

325
00:20:29,311 --> 00:20:30,497
Good one!

326
00:20:32,700 --> 00:20:34,540
Are you Lord Li’s second son?

327
00:20:50,100 --> 00:20:51,140
What happened?

328
00:20:51,540 --> 00:20:52,380
How did you get hurt?

329
00:20:54,420 --> 00:20:55,180
I...

330
00:20:56,860 --> 00:20:58,580
I was taking a walk at the backyard

331
00:20:59,300 --> 00:21:00,700
and banged my head on a tree by accident.

332
00:21:00,700 --> 00:21:02,020
= Li Yonghe, courtesy name Shenli =

333
00:21:02,020 --> 00:21:02,980
Forgive me, Your Majesty.

334
00:21:03,740 --> 00:21:04,580
This boy...

335
00:21:05,900 --> 00:21:08,460
This boy is hopelessly stupid.

336
00:21:11,380 --> 00:21:12,660
Are there knickknacks

337
00:21:12,740 --> 00:21:13,740
suitable for him?

338
00:21:17,580 --> 00:21:19,260
I brought tasty desserts

339
00:21:20,820 --> 00:21:21,900
for Huirou.

340
00:21:22,460 --> 00:21:24,460
Bonehead! Apologize now.

341
00:21:24,740 --> 00:21:26,500
You can’t call princess by her name.

342
00:21:31,220 --> 00:21:32,460
A few years ago,

343
00:21:33,940 --> 00:21:35,420
I gave you a promise,

344
00:21:35,940 --> 00:21:37,860
but you didn’t know what you wanted.

345
00:21:39,740 --> 00:21:40,900
My...my father said

346
00:21:41,700 --> 00:21:43,140
Your Majesty

347
00:21:43,220 --> 00:21:44,740
had already given us too much.

348
00:21:44,940 --> 00:21:46,100
We should be content

349
00:21:46,900 --> 00:21:48,020
and can’t ask for more.

350
00:21:48,660 --> 00:21:49,700
Are you sure you don’t want anything?

351
00:21:53,260 --> 00:21:54,340
If I only allow you

352
00:21:54,700 --> 00:21:56,340
to call my daughter Huirou

353
00:21:56,340 --> 00:21:57,380
instead of princess,

354
00:21:58,140 --> 00:21:59,100
do you want it or not?

355
00:22:03,700 --> 00:22:04,700
- You can’t call princess’s name! - I want it.

356
00:22:04,700 --> 00:22:05,700
Yes.

357
00:22:06,340 --> 00:22:07,140
I do.

358
00:22:07,700 --> 00:22:09,740
I... Thank you, Your Majesty.

359
00:22:10,500 --> 00:22:11,940
Thank you, Your Majesty. I want it!

360
00:22:12,260 --> 00:22:13,140
Thank you, Your Majesty.

361
00:22:14,140 --> 00:22:15,060
I want it!

362
00:22:29,140 --> 00:22:29,900
Huaiji,

363
00:22:31,420 --> 00:22:34,300
will father pick Cousin Ping

364
00:22:35,100 --> 00:22:37,860
to be my husband?

365
00:23:13,820 --> 00:23:14,660
Your Majesty,

366
00:23:16,580 --> 00:23:17,660
Huirou is still young.

367
00:23:18,540 --> 00:23:21,460
It’s too early to decide on her husband now.

368
00:23:22,700 --> 00:23:24,460
Wait till Li Wei grows up

369
00:23:24,980 --> 00:23:26,060
and see if he’s good enough.

370
00:23:29,820 --> 00:23:31,460
I didn’t mean to rush into it,

371
00:23:32,540 --> 00:23:35,300
but I just realized,

372
00:23:37,260 --> 00:23:38,340
Huirou

373
00:23:39,140 --> 00:23:41,020
is as pure as crystal.

374
00:23:41,140 --> 00:23:42,500
She doesn’t know how evil men can be.

375
00:23:44,340 --> 00:23:45,420
What if

376
00:23:46,780 --> 00:23:48,500
she loses her heart

377
00:23:48,500 --> 00:23:49,700
to an untrustworthy philanderer?

378
00:23:50,900 --> 00:23:51,780
Then

379
00:23:52,700 --> 00:23:54,780
she’ll end up as tragic as my aunt.

380
00:23:56,500 --> 00:23:57,460
If that happens,

381
00:23:59,580 --> 00:24:01,180
I won’t act like father.

382
00:24:02,820 --> 00:24:03,940
I’ll kill his entire clan!

383
00:24:09,700 --> 00:24:10,900
They’re still kids.

384
00:24:11,940 --> 00:24:13,140
How...how come...

385
00:24:14,340 --> 00:24:15,180
How come...

386
00:24:20,100 --> 00:24:21,740
Other families don’t matter,

387
00:24:23,940 --> 00:24:24,740
but Empress,

388
00:24:28,740 --> 00:24:30,140
I don’t want you and me...

389
00:24:42,740 --> 00:24:44,220
I’m grateful

390
00:24:46,500 --> 00:24:47,980
for Your Majesty’s concern.

391
00:25:06,140 --> 00:25:07,780
Prime Minister Xia, aren’t you too sick

392
00:25:07,780 --> 00:25:08,740
to work?

393
00:25:09,460 --> 00:25:12,060
How come you’re watching them dancing
in broad daylight

394
00:25:13,140 --> 00:25:15,380
in the forbidden Hu dresses?

395
00:25:20,420 --> 00:25:21,460
You’re the expert.

396
00:25:22,300 --> 00:25:23,820
Look at this exotic dance.

397
00:25:24,300 --> 00:25:26,900
Why do I find it boring?

398
00:25:28,980 --> 00:25:30,020
Boring?

399
00:25:31,100 --> 00:25:32,620
You took sick leave

400
00:25:33,420 --> 00:25:35,060
to entertain yourself.

401
00:25:35,620 --> 00:25:37,740
Are you giving censors a reason

402
00:25:37,740 --> 00:25:39,420
to criticize you?

403
00:25:39,620 --> 00:25:40,580
Of course.

404
00:25:43,460 --> 00:25:46,060
His Majesty meant to appoint me Prime Minister.

405
00:25:46,940 --> 00:25:48,260
Wang Gongchen stated

406
00:25:48,900 --> 00:25:51,060
that united officials can work more efficiently.

407
00:25:51,740 --> 00:25:53,500
I argued

408
00:25:54,060 --> 00:25:55,940
with Zhizhong in Guanzhong,

409
00:25:55,940 --> 00:25:57,220
so we shouldn’t work together.

410
00:25:57,620 --> 00:25:58,740
Then His Majesty took his advice.

411
00:25:59,620 --> 00:26:01,540
I’m the victim here.

412
00:26:02,100 --> 00:26:04,300
I’m only watching the dance for relaxation.

413
00:26:04,420 --> 00:26:05,860
However harsh they criticize me,

414
00:26:05,860 --> 00:26:07,300
His Majesty will ignore it.

415
00:26:12,540 --> 00:26:14,020
Isn’t Wang Gongchen

416
00:26:14,420 --> 00:26:15,860
always acting against Ouyang Xiu

417
00:26:15,900 --> 00:26:17,580
and Fan Zhongyan?

418
00:26:18,300 --> 00:26:19,780
He took

419
00:26:20,300 --> 00:26:22,020
those so-called gentlemen down

420
00:26:22,020 --> 00:26:22,860
simply with a banquet.

421
00:26:23,180 --> 00:26:23,860
How come

422
00:26:24,180 --> 00:26:25,740
he targeted at you all of a sudden?

423
00:26:30,340 --> 00:26:33,180
He’s exactly what His Majesty called

424
00:26:33,180 --> 00:26:35,620
fishing for fame.

425
00:26:36,740 --> 00:26:38,940
He held personal grudges

426
00:26:39,140 --> 00:26:41,420
against Ouyang Xiu and Su Shunqin,

427
00:26:41,420 --> 00:26:43,620
and took revenge on them

428
00:26:44,340 --> 00:26:45,860
in the name of justice and loyalty.

429
00:26:45,860 --> 00:26:47,980
Then he was afraid to be regarded as my ally,

430
00:26:47,980 --> 00:26:49,380
so he was eager to cut ties with me.

431
00:26:51,620 --> 00:26:52,620
Is condemning me

432
00:26:52,620 --> 00:26:53,740
making him innocent of cliquism?

433
00:26:53,820 --> 00:26:54,860
Ridiculous!

434
00:27:15,940 --> 00:27:17,060
Something has been confusing me

435
00:27:17,060 --> 00:27:18,100
for long.

436
00:27:19,620 --> 00:27:22,380
Those gentlemen think you’re evil,

437
00:27:23,180 --> 00:27:24,380
but I sense

438
00:27:26,300 --> 00:27:27,180
that His Majesty

439
00:27:27,180 --> 00:27:29,100
doesn’t despise you.

440
00:27:31,940 --> 00:27:34,420
You think His Majesty

441
00:27:34,540 --> 00:27:36,780
like those conceited brats

442
00:27:37,580 --> 00:27:38,500
who always lecture him

443
00:27:38,500 --> 00:27:40,100
with virtues and ethics

444
00:27:40,420 --> 00:27:42,220
and force him to be a saint?

445
00:27:44,780 --> 00:27:46,940
His Majesty detests them but can’t scold

446
00:27:47,020 --> 00:27:48,060
or punish them.

447
00:27:49,100 --> 00:27:52,460
Compared with them,

448
00:27:52,460 --> 00:27:53,660
I’m talented

449
00:27:53,660 --> 00:27:55,260
and capable

450
00:27:55,700 --> 00:27:56,940
and I’m more considerate.

451
00:27:58,220 --> 00:28:00,860
Of course His Majesty doesn’t despise me.

452
00:28:00,900 --> 00:28:01,660
What do you think?

453
00:28:05,980 --> 00:28:07,740
Yuanhao died after his son Ninglingge

454
00:28:07,740 --> 00:28:08,900
cut off his nose.

455
00:28:08,900 --> 00:28:09,860
Xixia is in chaos.

456
00:28:10,140 --> 00:28:11,860
According to Yuanhao’s will,

457
00:28:12,140 --> 00:28:13,820
= Chen Zhizhong, courtesy name Zhaoyu =
his brother Weigeningling should be the successor,

458
00:28:14,500 --> 00:28:15,820
but the tribes are against him.

459
00:28:16,260 --> 00:28:18,260
It’s said that Mozang is pregnant.

460
00:28:18,740 --> 00:28:19,580
The tribes intend

461
00:28:19,580 --> 00:28:21,660
to have her son ascend the throne.

462
00:28:22,220 --> 00:28:25,180
Now, both Weigeningling and Mozang

463
00:28:25,740 --> 00:28:27,860
are asking us to confer the title on them.

464
00:28:29,220 --> 00:28:30,100
The thing is,

465
00:28:30,580 --> 00:28:32,900
Yuanhao died in his own son’s hand.

466
00:28:33,100 --> 00:28:34,300
Both sides’

467
00:28:34,300 --> 00:28:35,660
= Yu Zhouxun, courtesy name Yuzhi =
competing for the throne are selfish.

468
00:28:36,100 --> 00:28:37,460
We should sit and watch

469
00:28:37,700 --> 00:28:40,460
and show no favor to any of them.

470
00:28:40,660 --> 00:28:41,420
I disagree.

471
00:28:41,820 --> 00:28:43,740
= Wen Yanbo, courtesy name Kuanfu =
I believe

472
00:28:43,900 --> 00:28:45,180
crowning Mozang’s son

473
00:28:45,300 --> 00:28:46,620
will benefit us more.

474
00:28:47,100 --> 00:28:48,140
He’s still too young,

475
00:28:48,220 --> 00:28:49,740
so the three tribes will take charge together.

476
00:28:49,820 --> 00:28:51,100
We can appoint all their chiefs

477
00:28:51,100 --> 00:28:52,420
governor.

478
00:28:52,860 --> 00:28:55,100
Once they’re divided, their strength will weaken.

479
00:28:55,220 --> 00:28:57,180
Then our west border will be in peace.

480
00:28:57,580 --> 00:28:58,580
I beg to differ.

481
00:28:59,220 --> 00:29:01,020
= Wang Gongchen, courtesy name Junkuang =
Taking advantage of others’ losses

482
00:29:01,420 --> 00:29:02,460
is immoral.

483
00:29:03,340 --> 00:29:04,900
Your Majesty is a benevolent emperor.

484
00:29:05,740 --> 00:29:07,460
How can we manipulate a widow and her son?

485
00:29:07,820 --> 00:29:10,140
Those barbarians are sneaky and ruthless.

486
00:29:11,140 --> 00:29:12,220
If not manipulate them,

487
00:29:12,700 --> 00:29:12,980
are you planning

488
00:29:13,020 --> 00:29:14,660
to civilize them?

489
00:29:16,500 --> 00:29:17,780
Their loss today

490
00:29:18,060 --> 00:29:19,700
is caused by immorality.

491
00:29:19,980 --> 00:29:22,260
Yuanhao abandoned his wife and son

492
00:29:22,420 --> 00:29:23,580
and married his daughter-in-law.

493
00:29:23,740 --> 00:29:24,740
He had this coming.

494
00:29:25,060 --> 00:29:27,300
Under a tyrant and coldblooded father,

495
00:29:27,660 --> 00:29:29,860
officials are disloyal; sons are unfilial.

496
00:29:30,380 --> 00:29:31,900
Ethics are disregarded; rules are ignored.

497
00:29:32,020 --> 00:29:32,980
How can they grow stronger

498
00:29:33,060 --> 00:29:33,820
and pose a threat to us?

499
00:29:33,820 --> 00:29:34,460
You...

500
00:29:40,300 --> 00:29:44,500
I’m benevolent.

501
00:29:53,620 --> 00:29:55,660
As ruthless

502
00:29:55,780 --> 00:29:56,860
and immoral as Yuanhao was,

503
00:29:58,100 --> 00:30:01,140
why could he still win so many battles

504
00:30:01,140 --> 00:30:02,180
and govern a vast land?

505
00:30:04,620 --> 00:30:05,900
Countless people suffered

506
00:30:06,340 --> 00:30:08,060
from his wrongdoings.

507
00:30:09,300 --> 00:30:11,260
Although he was killed by his son,

508
00:30:12,060 --> 00:30:13,620
another is about to be born.

509
00:30:14,380 --> 00:30:16,780
I’m more benevolent than him,

510
00:30:17,420 --> 00:30:18,820
yet my children died one after another.

511
00:30:19,060 --> 00:30:21,500
Up to now, I still don’t have an heir.

512
00:30:26,980 --> 00:30:28,180
Your Majesty

513
00:30:28,580 --> 00:30:30,500
cares about the masses and officials

514
00:30:30,500 --> 00:30:31,580
and will be blessed

515
00:30:31,980 --> 00:30:34,540
with...with lots and lots of children.

516
00:30:35,460 --> 00:30:37,660
Your Majesty is still in your prime.

517
00:30:37,660 --> 00:30:39,780
The Empress is fair and the harem is harmonious.

518
00:30:40,620 --> 00:30:42,660
There are more sons to come.

519
00:30:43,060 --> 00:30:43,820
Yes.

520
00:30:44,180 --> 00:30:46,100
The late Emperor had Your Majesty at 42.

521
00:30:46,380 --> 00:30:48,140
The Emperor before him
had The Eighth Prince at 47.

522
00:30:48,460 --> 00:30:50,260
Your Majesty are blessed

523
00:30:50,420 --> 00:30:52,380
and will have your own sons.

524
00:30:52,780 --> 00:30:55,700
Your Majesty will have your own sons.

525
00:31:02,820 --> 00:31:03,900
I think so.

526
00:31:07,060 --> 00:31:08,380
I’m always dedicated.

527
00:31:08,860 --> 00:31:10,100
I may not be a great emperor,

528
00:31:10,540 --> 00:31:11,700
but I love my people.

529
00:31:12,100 --> 00:31:14,980
Heaven won’t make me heirless.

530
00:31:21,260 --> 00:31:22,340
As for these proposals persuading me

531
00:31:22,460 --> 00:31:24,460
to promote Zongshi to Crown Prince

532
00:31:25,100 --> 00:31:28,180
or adopt more sons

533
00:31:28,180 --> 00:31:29,140
from other royal family members,

534
00:31:30,940 --> 00:31:32,380
you can have them back.

535
00:31:35,340 --> 00:31:37,060
Yes, Your Majesty.

536
00:31:42,140 --> 00:31:43,700
Benefiting from others’ losses

537
00:31:44,060 --> 00:31:45,260
is unethical.

538
00:31:46,140 --> 00:31:47,620
Yuanhao’s death

539
00:31:48,140 --> 00:31:49,140
and his son’s execution

540
00:31:49,620 --> 00:31:50,540
are giving rise to chaos.

541
00:31:51,340 --> 00:31:53,500
Whether it’s the three tribes or Yuanhao’s brother

542
00:31:54,020 --> 00:31:55,620
that will take over the leadership

543
00:31:56,180 --> 00:31:57,260
is their internal affair.

544
00:31:57,340 --> 00:31:58,620
Let’s stay out of it.

545
00:32:00,220 --> 00:32:02,220
Tighten the security at the border.

546
00:32:02,220 --> 00:32:03,220
Add more patrols

547
00:32:03,540 --> 00:32:05,580
in case fugitives

548
00:32:05,580 --> 00:32:06,540
harass our border

549
00:32:06,940 --> 00:32:08,940
and rob our people.

550
00:32:16,900 --> 00:32:18,420
You monitored that place for days

551
00:32:18,420 --> 00:32:19,540
but didn’t find anything suspicious?

552
00:32:20,180 --> 00:32:21,500
You didn’t see a girl there

553
00:32:21,500 --> 00:32:22,860
who looks like the maid in the painting?

554
00:32:23,580 --> 00:32:24,380
This month,

555
00:32:24,380 --> 00:32:25,860
Zhang Maoze went there a few times.

556
00:32:25,940 --> 00:32:27,580
Other than that, nothing is special.

557
00:32:30,340 --> 00:32:31,540
A few times.

558
00:32:33,820 --> 00:32:36,100
He went there a few times in a month.

559
00:32:36,300 --> 00:32:37,380
There must be a reason.

560
00:32:40,060 --> 00:32:41,780
Over the past year, he’s been poking around

561
00:32:41,780 --> 00:32:44,060
about The Fourth Princess’s death.

562
00:32:44,060 --> 00:32:45,460
What is he up to?

563
00:32:51,380 --> 00:32:53,300
I told you

564
00:32:53,300 --> 00:32:55,340
to be my eyes and ears

565
00:32:55,700 --> 00:32:57,380
to see and hear everything.

566
00:32:57,980 --> 00:32:58,740
But what now?

567
00:32:59,220 --> 00:33:00,820
You’re blind and deaf!

568
00:33:03,460 --> 00:33:04,500
Deputy Officer Yang, there’s one more thing

569
00:33:04,500 --> 00:33:06,740
that I’m not sure if I should tell you.

570
00:33:06,740 --> 00:33:07,940
Cut the crap. Say it.

571
00:33:08,380 --> 00:33:09,420
On our off day earlier,

572
00:33:09,500 --> 00:33:11,020
we agreed to drink together

573
00:33:11,020 --> 00:33:11,980
and pooled our money

574
00:33:12,060 --> 00:33:12,980
to go to Winehouse Fan

575
00:33:12,980 --> 00:33:14,540
to watch the new singer’s show.

576
00:33:14,860 --> 00:33:16,980
But Yan Xiu didn’t come.

577
00:33:16,980 --> 00:33:18,780
He loved drinking

578
00:33:18,780 --> 00:33:19,540
and watching the shows.

579
00:33:20,140 --> 00:33:21,260
Chen told me

580
00:33:21,460 --> 00:33:22,740
he’s got lucky lately,

581
00:33:23,420 --> 00:33:24,340
saying he’s been intimate

582
00:33:24,340 --> 00:33:25,860
with the Empress’s maid Ling’er.

583
00:33:26,380 --> 00:33:27,340
I don’t know if that’s true

584
00:33:27,780 --> 00:33:29,020
or he made that up.

585
00:33:36,260 --> 00:33:36,980
I see.

586
00:33:40,260 --> 00:33:41,820
You can stop going there.

587
00:33:43,460 --> 00:33:45,660
Keep a close eye on Yan Xiu.

588
00:33:50,060 --> 00:33:52,780
Remember to be discreet.

589
00:33:53,260 --> 00:33:54,620
Don’t let anyone find out.

590
00:34:04,380 --> 00:34:05,140
Taste it.

591
00:34:06,820 --> 00:34:07,900
Is it the same

592
00:34:07,900 --> 00:34:08,900
as what you had when you were little?

593
00:34:11,260 --> 00:34:13,380
It’s made by a chef I hired from the south.

594
00:34:21,020 --> 00:34:22,580
Why did you ask me to come?

595
00:34:23,740 --> 00:34:25,420
Not just to let me

596
00:34:25,420 --> 00:34:26,380
taste the dessert, right?

597
00:34:27,300 --> 00:34:29,260
Business can wait.

598
00:34:29,820 --> 00:34:30,900
Have some desserts first.

599
00:34:34,500 --> 00:34:35,260
What is it?

600
00:34:38,460 --> 00:34:39,580
I want to be in the Cabinet

601
00:34:39,980 --> 00:34:42,020
and be called Prime Minister Xia.

602
00:34:45,020 --> 00:34:46,300
I know.

603
00:34:47,780 --> 00:34:48,860
That’s your goal all along.

604
00:34:50,540 --> 00:34:51,540
When you were young, you were confident

605
00:34:51,540 --> 00:34:52,700
that you’d become a Prime Minister one day.

606
00:34:53,700 --> 00:34:55,060
Yet here you are over 60.

607
00:34:55,620 --> 00:34:57,260
Finally, you were given the chance

608
00:34:58,580 --> 00:35:00,060
but censors ruined it.

609
00:35:06,820 --> 00:35:08,380
I was already a famous poet

610
00:35:08,780 --> 00:35:09,980
and an all-round talent as a teenager.

611
00:35:11,060 --> 00:35:14,220
At 20, I had the potential to be a Prime Minister.

612
00:35:17,460 --> 00:35:20,140
Sadly, my father died on the battlefield.

613
00:35:21,380 --> 00:35:22,900
The late Emperor’s compensation

614
00:35:23,180 --> 00:35:23,860
was a marriage

615
00:35:23,900 --> 00:35:25,900
that cost me the rest of my life.

616
00:35:30,500 --> 00:35:31,420
I believed

617
00:35:32,820 --> 00:35:34,100
with my talent,

618
00:35:35,260 --> 00:35:37,500
I’d become powerful

619
00:35:39,220 --> 00:35:41,020
and marry the woman I love.

620
00:35:46,340 --> 00:35:47,740
The past is the past.

621
00:35:50,660 --> 00:35:51,700
Stop thinking about it.

622
00:35:56,500 --> 00:35:57,820
When I was a local governor,

623
00:35:58,500 --> 00:36:01,100
I removed witchcraft, promoted medicine, farming,

624
00:36:02,100 --> 00:36:04,780
battled disasters, saved lives and built bridges.

625
00:36:05,820 --> 00:36:06,660
When leading the troops,

626
00:36:07,060 --> 00:36:09,140
I was well aware of the situation in the west.

627
00:36:09,820 --> 00:36:11,500
Looking back, all my strategies

628
00:36:11,500 --> 00:36:12,420
have been proven right.

629
00:36:12,420 --> 00:36:13,580
Why couldn’t I become the Prime Minister?

630
00:36:18,860 --> 00:36:21,500
Simply because of my failed marriage?

631
00:36:23,180 --> 00:36:24,100
Who could live happily

632
00:36:24,140 --> 00:36:25,180
with a shrew

633
00:36:25,180 --> 00:36:26,340
given by the late Emperor?

634
00:36:32,380 --> 00:36:34,100
Just because I’m sophisticated,

635
00:36:35,340 --> 00:36:37,180
that geezer Shi Jie

636
00:36:37,180 --> 00:36:38,340
called me corrupted.

637
00:36:39,620 --> 00:36:40,620
My achievements

638
00:36:40,660 --> 00:36:41,980
are ten times better than his.

639
00:36:42,020 --> 00:36:42,740
Enough.

640
00:36:45,260 --> 00:36:46,500
He’s dead

641
00:36:47,460 --> 00:36:49,260
and almost got whipped by you after death.

642
00:36:49,700 --> 00:36:50,780
Don’t be too mad.

643
00:37:01,940 --> 00:37:03,100
Before I die,

644
00:37:05,700 --> 00:37:06,940
I will make everyone,

645
00:37:08,900 --> 00:37:11,300
especially those self-claimed gentlemen,

646
00:37:12,660 --> 00:37:13,860
call me Prime Minister Xia

647
00:37:13,860 --> 00:37:15,460
with respect.

648
00:37:33,220 --> 00:37:33,820
I know

649
00:37:33,820 --> 00:37:35,380
that’s your aspiration all along.

650
00:37:37,820 --> 00:37:41,140
You’ve made arrangements

651
00:37:42,300 --> 00:37:43,940
in and out of the court all these years.

652
00:37:44,860 --> 00:37:46,100
Currently,

653
00:37:48,140 --> 00:37:49,780
although Madam Zhang is favored

654
00:37:50,540 --> 00:37:52,460
even more by His Majesty,

655
00:37:52,460 --> 00:37:54,420
she’s become less ambitious.

656
00:37:57,500 --> 00:37:59,180
Poor woman!

657
00:38:01,900 --> 00:38:03,580
She gave birth to three girls

658
00:38:05,260 --> 00:38:06,460
but lost them one by one.

659
00:38:07,620 --> 00:38:09,660
Physical and mental sufferings

660
00:38:11,260 --> 00:38:12,660
almost broke her.

661
00:38:15,020 --> 00:38:17,340
It’s her love for His Majesty

662
00:38:17,580 --> 00:38:18,940
that supports her to live this long.

663
00:38:19,860 --> 00:38:20,660
But...

664
00:38:22,140 --> 00:38:23,860
If you want her to fight for more...

665
00:38:34,500 --> 00:38:35,980
Lantiao is pregnant.

666
00:38:37,980 --> 00:38:39,780
But Zhang Maoze is investigating

667
00:38:39,780 --> 00:38:41,540
that paper mulberry flower powder thing again.

668
00:38:46,060 --> 00:38:47,700
Lantiao is calculative.

669
00:38:48,540 --> 00:38:49,940
She contacted me behind your back

670
00:38:49,940 --> 00:38:51,620
a long time ago.

671
00:38:56,820 --> 00:38:57,900
I know what I’m doing.

672
00:39:31,500 --> 00:39:33,380
I’ve been looking for a fine piece of jade for you

673
00:39:33,780 --> 00:39:35,620
and finally found it after years of effort.

674
00:39:36,100 --> 00:39:37,860
This jade is over a thousand years old.

675
00:39:38,380 --> 00:39:40,460
It’s much more valuable

676
00:39:40,460 --> 00:39:41,540
than common jewelry

677
00:39:42,380 --> 00:39:43,820
or treasures

678
00:39:43,820 --> 00:39:45,620
stored in our private mansion.

679
00:39:47,740 --> 00:39:48,580
This...

680
00:39:50,020 --> 00:39:51,740
Ever since I got married that year,

681
00:39:52,340 --> 00:39:53,660
I’ve been saying to myself

682
00:39:54,700 --> 00:39:57,300
that once I’m powerful enough,

683
00:39:58,100 --> 00:39:59,780
I’ll marry or divorce any woman

684
00:39:59,780 --> 00:40:00,860
as I please.

685
00:40:02,500 --> 00:40:03,460
In the end,

686
00:40:03,460 --> 00:40:05,180
I have a house of concubines

687
00:40:06,420 --> 00:40:10,380
but don’t get to see you often.

688
00:40:12,740 --> 00:40:14,980
Your wife lost her mind

689
00:40:16,940 --> 00:40:18,380
partly because of me.

690
00:40:18,900 --> 00:40:20,540
She stole your man.

691
00:40:21,220 --> 00:40:22,780
Instead of taking revenge on her

692
00:40:22,780 --> 00:40:24,060
or kicking her out,

693
00:40:24,380 --> 00:40:26,300
you want her to have a happy marriage?

694
00:40:32,140 --> 00:40:33,740
I didn’t expect it’d turn out so bad

695
00:40:35,180 --> 00:40:36,820
that you’d be laughed at by your colleagues

696
00:40:37,420 --> 00:40:38,660
and lose your promotion.

697
00:40:39,740 --> 00:40:41,100
At this stage,

698
00:40:41,100 --> 00:40:42,260
all that isn’t important.

699
00:40:42,940 --> 00:40:43,980
The truth is,

700
00:40:43,980 --> 00:40:45,460
I ruined your entire life

701
00:40:45,620 --> 00:40:47,300
but you never blamed me.

702
00:40:50,820 --> 00:40:51,700
Rest assured.

703
00:40:52,620 --> 00:40:53,780
Although we can’t be together

704
00:40:54,100 --> 00:40:56,180
for the rest of our lives,

705
00:40:56,900 --> 00:41:00,220
we each must live a glorious life.

706
00:41:12,460 --> 00:41:13,540
Deputy Officer Yang.

707
00:41:15,740 --> 00:41:18,220
I’m here to ask you something, Pingfu.

708
00:41:19,540 --> 00:41:20,860
I’m all ears.

709
00:41:21,460 --> 00:41:24,140
Are you investigating The Fourth Princess’s death?

710
00:41:25,460 --> 00:41:27,260
The Agency is responsible for it

711
00:41:27,260 --> 00:41:29,460
but I know you’re leading the investigation.

712
00:41:29,940 --> 00:41:31,580
How could I interfere?

713
00:41:34,380 --> 00:41:35,860
I heard over the past six months,

714
00:41:35,900 --> 00:41:37,940
you requested all her medical records.

715
00:41:38,700 --> 00:41:40,340
If you aren’t investigating her death,

716
00:41:40,580 --> 00:41:41,900
are you

717
00:41:41,900 --> 00:41:43,940
studying medicine?

718
00:41:47,740 --> 00:41:48,940
= The Yellow Emperor’s Inner Canon =

719
00:41:49,980 --> 00:41:50,740
I am.

720
00:41:51,740 --> 00:41:54,980
I’m always passionate about it.

721
00:41:55,860 --> 00:41:57,540
You probably don’t know

722
00:41:58,140 --> 00:42:00,180
many servants and eunuchs

723
00:42:00,740 --> 00:42:01,900
come to me for acupuncture

724
00:42:01,900 --> 00:42:03,420
when they have headaches

725
00:42:03,540 --> 00:42:05,620
or back and leg pains.

726
00:42:09,780 --> 00:42:12,140
Speaking of The Fourth Princess’s sudden death,

727
00:42:12,940 --> 00:42:14,780
the Imperial Hospital determined

728
00:42:14,780 --> 00:42:15,900
the cause of death as an asthmatic attack

729
00:42:16,140 --> 00:42:18,580
instead of poison or injury.

730
00:42:19,660 --> 00:42:21,060
As for the two maids on duty,

731
00:42:21,340 --> 00:42:22,620
one was cornered by you,

732
00:42:22,620 --> 00:42:24,580
and then drowned herself in the lake.

733
00:42:25,100 --> 00:42:27,140
The other one escaped.

734
00:42:28,540 --> 00:42:30,740
You’ve been looking for her

735
00:42:30,740 --> 00:42:32,020
for three years.

736
00:42:32,660 --> 00:42:35,740
Have you found any trace of her?

737
00:42:41,900 --> 00:42:44,780
It’s not your concern.

738
00:42:46,580 --> 00:42:47,300
Yes.

739
00:43:03,780 --> 00:43:10,780
♪ Memory is the breath of deep sleep ♪

740
00:43:11,340 --> 00:43:18,220
♪ It emerges in every crevice ♪

741
00:43:18,700 --> 00:43:25,060
♪ Shallow dreams are like
copper bells under eaves ♪

742
00:43:25,500 --> 00:43:32,260
♪ Woken up when the wind blows ♪

743
00:43:33,500 --> 00:43:40,300
♪ Fate is predetermined ♪

744
00:43:40,900 --> 00:43:47,660
♪ Struggle to break out of it ♪

745
00:43:48,220 --> 00:43:55,260
♪ Who will battle fate with me ♪

746
00:43:55,260 --> 00:44:02,060
♪ Regardless of the ending ♪

747
00:44:06,940 --> 00:44:10,460
♪ Peach branches shake in the spring breeze ♪

748
00:44:10,660 --> 00:44:14,260
♪ Walls sigh, the wind is silent ♪

749
00:44:14,260 --> 00:44:17,460
♪ The boy beside the wall is unaware of it ♪

750
00:44:17,460 --> 00:44:21,860
♪ He plays with the butterfly, gathering honey ♪

751
00:44:21,860 --> 00:44:25,580
♪ Peach blossoms tell a love story ♪

752
00:44:25,580 --> 00:44:29,140
♪ About a couple who lives happily ♪

753
00:44:29,140 --> 00:44:32,860
♪ Unluckily deep love comes to nowhere ♪

754
00:44:32,860 --> 00:44:38,620
♪ All fated,
drawing Double Happiness in autumn ♪

755
00:44:40,420 --> 00:44:43,540
♪ Peach branches shake in the spring breeze ♪

756
00:44:44,060 --> 00:44:47,420
♪ Walls sigh, the wind is silent ♪

